          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "PAL offloads computation to "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "generated code",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " executed in a sandbox — the model writes Python (or similar) instead of doing arithmetic or logic in prose."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What it is"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Model outputs code; runtime executes; result is fed back or used as final answer. Reduces calculation errors in agent analytics steps."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "codeBlock",
        "attrs": {
          "language": "python"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "# Model generates:\ntotal = sum(prices) * (1 - discount)\nprint(total)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Why it matters for agents"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Agent systems use advanced reasoning prompts when single-pass CoT is insufficient — complex planning, search problems, or verification-heavy workflows."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Trade-offs"
